post.description:
Request a vendor questionnaire to be sent to one or more nominated email addresses.
Vendor must be already monitored in UpGuard.

Required API key permissions: `VendorRisk` (select when creating API key in Account Settings)

The following merge tags are supported for email_title and email_subject text:
+ Vendor name {{VendorName}}
+ Account name {{AccountName}}
+ Questionnaire type {{QuestionnaireType}}
